{"tid":2384281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佐敦淪疫區 市民：領導班子唔掂","createTime":"2021-01-28T12:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T12:51:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7171045f905535a2e53f8827676963f3982638db","tid":2384281,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:51:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210128/2ISYFCSPF5GVFNPG7BUKRAHU6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210128%2F2ISYFCSPF5GVFNPG7BUKRAHU6E%2F&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUkx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=b1d83f76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210128%2F2ISYFCSPF5GVFNPG7BUKRAHU6E%2F&h=f224f6dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210128/2ISYFCSPF5GVFNPG7BUKRAHU6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n佐敦淪疫區 市民：領導班子唔掂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dwlrocUiKK5A5jSluD1VK4lw1cQ=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IFG5FX7VABE4FGVQOWPTBDBQY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdwlrocUiKK5A5jSluD1VK4lw1cQ%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIFG5FX7VABE4FGVQOWPTBDBQY4.jpg&h=ffcd7305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■文耀樓是其中一幢前日深夜列入強檢名單的大廈，昨有人在平台打掃。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武肺疫情繼續失控擴散，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭煩死人 紅磡防突閘  長生店「走鬼」搬壽衣<br />\n<br />\n佐敦新增五幢強檢大廈，為。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n雖然「八文樓」大廈。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：粥店、酒店爆疫 紅磡13人中招  當局高調宣佈 區議員：或突襲封區<br />\n<br />\n疫情持續一年未解決，市民Jason指原因在於「封到頭又封唔到尾，封到尾又封唔到頭」，政府責無旁貸，「成個領導班子都唔掂，唔好話淨係林鄭一個，咩局長咩領導班子都唔得。點樣徹底（抗疫）？全部炒晒佢。」在區內工作的田先生亦擔心居住地區遲早會被突襲式封鎖，怒斥政府封區行動「黐線！佢都儍嘅，冇腦做嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n居住文華樓高。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4k10pmsy3PXAFrgFOHjTJlc_rVA=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MRR3IV4Q6BGBLIYNM3ZZTXSVWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4k10pmsy3PXAFrgFOHjTJlc_rVA%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMRR3IV4Q6BGBLIYNM3ZZTXSVWU.jpg&h=e4e79a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■位於深水埗疫廈的食肆近日生意大跌，憂突擊封區血本無歸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食肆生意慘淡 冀獲補貼<br />\n<br />\n同是舊樓林立、多達38幢大廈須強檢的深水埗區情況更嚴峻，汝州街與南昌街。。。。。<br />\n。。"}]}